🚲 Dream Bike

Build it before you buy it.

Dream Bike is a next-generation e-bike builder inspired by PCPartPicker. It allows riders to build, customize, compare, and share their dream e-bike before purchasing any parts.

Vision

Dream Bike will become the best platform for planning custom e-bike builds.

Users will be able to:

* Build bikes in 3D
* Swap every compatible part
* Check compatibility instantly
* Estimate speed, range, and weight
* Compare builds
* Save builds to their Garage
* Share builds with the community
* Request new bike models
* Track build costs
* Plan future upgrades

Supported Bikes (Version 1)

Razor

* MX350
* MX400
* MX500
* MX650
* SX500
* RSF650

Future support will include additional brands and models as the compatibility database grows.

Core Features

* Interactive 3D bike builder
* Parts database
* Compatibility engine
* Performance calculator
* Community builds
* Garage
* Marketplace
* Request a Bike
* Beginner and Expert modes
* Build comparison
* Dream Score

Project Goal

Build the world’s best e-bike customization platform.

Every decision should make Dream Bike easier to use, more accurate, and more helpful for riders of every experience level.
